游戏中。</p><p> PC对<em>头骨和骨骼</em>的要求在下面可以看到： </p><figure id="attachment_3577614" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577614" style="width: 2271px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577614" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements.jpg" alt="“头骨和骨头” Beta PC要求" width="2271" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements.jpg 2271w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements-400x224.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements-800x447.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements-696x389.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements-1392x778.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skull-Bones-PC-Requirements-1068x597.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2271px) 100vw, 2271px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577614" class="wp-caption-text"> “ Skull＆Bones” Beta PC要求。图片来源：Ubisoft</figcaption></figure><p> Ubisoft还分享了一个预告片，详细介绍了<em>Skull＆Bones</em>的第一年，标题为Kingpins年。</p><p>本赛季将分为四个不同的章节（狂暴的潮汐，破坏的合唱，龙的唤醒和深处的阴影），每个章节都提供独特的奖励，突袭战和限时活动。还计划在本赛季后半赛季进行两种生活质量更新。<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x2V6UrJg0p8">在这里</a>查看预告片。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metroid-inspired-berserk-boy-announced-for-nintendo-switch-and-pc-3577049">宣布了</a>受<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/mega-man"><em>巨型男子</em></a>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/metroid">Metroid</a></em>启发的高速2D平台游戏的<em>Berserk Boy</em> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/skull-bones-announces-open-beta-and-first-year-roadmap-3577610">“ Skull＆Bones”帖子宣布开放Beta，第一年的路线图</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
